1.5
log
@Correct USE_X11 use.

NOTE: Setting USE_X11?=Yes in a Makefile.inc has no effect because it
will only be included after the MirPorts system Makefiles, so the
USE_X11?=No there will prevail.
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
# $MirOS: ports/x11/xfce4/desktop/Makefile.inc,v 1.4 2006/06/03 16:02:43 bsiegert Exp $
